# Academic Enterprise Overhaul — IMEC Research Platform

Complete transformation from "hacker/terminal" aesthetic to a multi-million-dollar Academic Enterprise platform (Bloomberg Graphics / WEF quality).

## Proposed Changes

### Design System & Layout

#### [MODIFY] [globals.css](file:///Users/ahmadghosn/IMEC%20Web/app/globals.css)
- **Remove**: Terminal cursor blink, scanlines overlay, pulse-dot, all hacker-style CSS
- **Add**: Google Fonts `Inter` (body/nav) + `Playfair Display` (headings/thesis text)
- **New palette**: `slate-950` background, `slate-100`/`slate-300` text, `blue-600`/`emerald-600` accents
- **Add**: Professional card styles, smooth transitions, toast animation

#### [MODIFY] [layout.tsx](file:///Users/ahmadghosn/IMEC%20Web/app/layout.tsx)
- Rename "IMEC INTELLIGENCE" → "IMEC Research Platform"
- Nav: "Command Center" → "Policy Aggregator", "Maps" → "Geospatial", "Dossier" → "Investigator"
- Remove noise texture overlay and radial glow
- Replace Geist font with Inter + Playfair Display
- Clean, professional header with subtle `border-slate-800` bottom border

