### API & Performance

#### [MODIFY] [route.ts](file:///Users/ahmadghosn/IMEC%20Web/app/api/intel/route.ts)
- Fetch from GNews API: `https://gnews.io/api/v4/search?q=IMEC+corridor+OR+India+Middle+East+trade&max=100&lang=en&apikey=KEY`
- Multiple parallel queries (4 queries × 100 results = 400 articles)
- Search terms: "IMEC corridor", "India Middle East trade", "Suez Canal disruption", "Belt Road Initiative"
- Fallback to existing curated data if API fails
- Return `{ articles: [...], source: 'live' | 'cached', error?: string }`

#### [NEW] [Toast.tsx](file:///Users/ahmadghosn/IMEC%20Web/components/Toast.tsx)
- Elegant slide-in toast notification
- Triggered when API falls back to cached data
- Design: `bg-amber-50 border-amber-200 text-amber-900` with dismiss button

#### [MODIFY] [IntelFeed.tsx](file:///Users/ahmadghosn/IMEC%20Web/components/IntelFeed.tsx)
- Install `@tanstack/react-virtual` for virtualized scrolling (handles 400+ articles smoothly)
- Scholarly card design: Playfair Display for titles, `Inter` for metadata
- Category badges: refined `bg-blue-50 text-blue-700` style (no neon colors)
- Date-sorted, most recent first
- Show toast when falling back to cached data

