### Disruption Simulator (New Feature)

#### [NEW] [DisruptionSimulator.tsx](file:///Users/ahmadghosn/IMEC%20Web/components/DisruptionSimulator.tsx)
- Professional panel with Playfair Display heading: "Economic Disruption Simulator"
- Draggable slider: "Suez Canal Traffic Disruption (%)" — range 0-100
- Three metric cards that update in real-time as slider moves:
  1. **IMEC Strategic Value Premium** — starts at 12%, rises to 87% at 100% disruption
  2. **Global Supply Chain Delay** — starts at 0 days, rises to 18.5 days
  3. **Overland Freight Surge** — starts at 0 TEUs, rises to 2.4M TEUs
- Smooth Framer Motion `animate` on the numbers (spring transitions)
- Economic model: nonlinear curves (quadratic/exponential) for realistic behavior
- Design: `bg-slate-900/80 border-slate-700` card, clean metric layout

